FuncDef:
The telnet ipv6 server disable command disables the IPv6 Telnet server service.
The undo telnet ipv6 server disable command enables the IPv6 Telnet server service. The telnet ipv6 server disable command disables the IPv6 Telnet server service. The undo telnet ipv6 server disable command enables the IPv6 Telnet server service. By default, IPv6 telnet server is enabled.
